 button area.\n49:      * Shows \"for Ship to Home\", \"for Ship To My Store\", etc.\n50:      */\n51:     readonly fulfillmentLabel: Locator;\n52: \n53:     // ── Store selector (In-Store Pickup) ──────────────────────────────────────\n54: \n55:     /**\n56:      * \"Set your store\" link shown in the Availability section when no store is set.\n57:      * Opens `dialog#store-selector`.\n58:      */\n59:     readonly setYourStoreLink: Locator;\n60: \n61:     /** Store-selector modal dialog */\n62:     readonly storeSelectorDialog: Locator;\n63: \n64:     /** Postal code / city search input inside the store selector dialog */\n65:     readonly storeSelectorSearchInput: Locator;\n66: \n67:     /** \"SEARCH STORES\" submit button inside the store selector dialog */\n68:     readonly storeSelectorSearchButton: Locator;\n69: \n70:     /**\n71:      * First \"Set Store\" button in the store selector results.\n72:      * UAT renders each result with a `button.primary-button` labelled \"Set Store\".\n73:      * Index 0 is the close button; index 1 onward are the store result CTA buttons.\n74:      */\n75:     readonly firstSetStoreButton: Locator;\n76: \n77:     // ── Postal code modal (Ship to Home) ──────────────────────────────────────\n78: \n79:     /**\n80:      * \"Change Postal Code\" link inside the Ship to Home section.\n81:      * Opens `dialog.modal` (a daisyUI `<dialog>`) for entering a delivery postal code.\n82:      */\n83:     readonly changePostalCodeLink: Locator;\n84: \n85:     /** Delivery location modal dialog (daisyUI: `<dialog class=\"modal\">`) */\n86:     readonly deliveryLocationModal: Locator;\n87: \n88:     /** Postal code text input inside the delivery location modal */\n89:     readonly postalCodeInput: Locator;\n90: \n91:     /**\n92:      * \"UPDATE DELIVERY LOCATION\" submit button in the delivery location modal.\n93:      * Identified by its `data-label` attribute which was confirmed on live UAT.\n94:      */\n95:     readonly updateDeliveryLocationButton: Locator;\n96: \n97:     // ── Add to Cart ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────\n98: \n99:     /** Add to Cart primary CTA button */\n100:     readonly addToCartButton: Locator;"}}
