[18:43:44] {"event": "tool_result", "tool": "view", "is_error": false, "result": {"status": "success", "file": "/Users/virginia.zambudio/PlaywrightAutomation/artifacts/outputs/quality-engineering-web-automation/validated-test-cases/DISCOVERY-SPEC-DISCOVERY-PLI-20260715.md", "content": "1: # DISCOVERY-SPEC-DISCOVERY-PLI-20260715\n2: \n3: ## Session\n4: - **Session ID:** DISCOVERY-PLI-20260715\n5: - **Date:** 2026-07-15\n6: - **Application:** London Drugs UAT — https://london-drugs-uat-origin.kibology.us/\n7: - **Scope:** Fix 6 failing tests via live selector discovery and timing analysis\n8: \n9: ---\n10: \n11: ## Findings — Selector Validation\n12: \n13: ### TC-83232 — Newsletter Signup (home-page.spec.ts)\n14: \n15: | Element | Selector | Confirmed |\n16: |---|---|---|\n17: | Email input | `div.bg-primary input[type=\"email\"]` | ✓ visible after scroll |\n18: | Submit button | `div.bg-primary button[type=\"submit\"]` (hasText `/sign up/i`) | ✓ present, **covered** by layout `div` |\n19: \n20: **Root causes identified:**\n21: 1. **(Chromium/Edge — original)** `waitFor({ state: 'visible', timeout: 30_000 })` at old line 414 was too short; fixed in working tree with 45s + retry loop.\n22: 2. **(Edge — new)** `newsletterSubmitButton.click()` silently failed because a layout `div` covered the button on Edge. Fix: `click({ force: true })`.\n23: \n24: **Live DOM evidence:**\n25: ```\n26: button text: \"SIGN UP\"\n27: button class: \"border-white-600 flex h-10 items-center justify-center rounded-none border-2 p-3\"\n28: covered by: DIV class=\"mx-auto hidden max-w-[1272px] flex-row items-center justify-between px-2 py-3 lg\"\n29: ```\n30: \n31: ---\n32: \n33: ### TC-83240 — Login (LoginPage.ts)\n34: \n35: | Element | Selector | Confirmed |\n36: |---|---|---|\n37: | Email input | `input[name=\"email\"][type=\"email\"]` | ✓ visible on `/auth/login` |\n38: | Password input | `input[name=\"password\"][type=\"password\"]` | ✓ |\n39: | Login button | `button[type=\"submit\"]` hasText `/login/i` | ✓ |\n40: \n41: **Root cause:**\n42: - **(Chromium — original)** Old code navigated to `/myaccount` (redirect chain); old timeout was 15s.\n43: - **(Edge — new)** After fixing to `/auth/login`, Edge got stuck on \"Loading...\" spinner. `BasePage.navigate()` (which calls `dismissLoadingIfStuck()` + `waitForAppShell()`) resolves the stuck state; added extra `body.click({ force: true })` before waiting for email input.\n44: \n45: ---\n46: \n47: ### TC-83238 — In-Store Pickup Store Selector (ProductDetailPage.ts)\n48: \n49: | Element | Selector | Confirmed |\n50: |---|---|---|\n51: | In-store pickup radio | `input[aria-label=\"Product Ship to Store Pickup Fulfillment Type\"]` | ✓ |\n52: | \"Set your store\" link | `p.cursor-pointer.text-primary` hasText `/set your store/i` | ✓ class: `mr-1 cursor-pointer text-primary underline` |\n53: | \"Check Availability\" link | `p.cursor-pointer` hasText `/check availability at other stores/i` | ✓ |\n54: | Store selector dialog | `dialog#store-selector` | ✓ |\n55: | Search input | `dialog#store-selector input[name=\"searchTerm\"]` | ✓ |\n56: | Search button | `dialog#store-selector button.primary-button` (first) | ✓ text: \"SEARCH STORES\" |\n57: | First Set Store button | `dialog#store-selector button.primary-button` (nth 1) | ✓ text: \"Set Store\" |\n58: \n59: **Root cause (Firefox/WebKit):**\n60: 1. **(Original)** Old `openStoreSelectorDialog` used single 15s wait → fixed with fallback logic in working tree.\n61: 2. **(New — after phase 1 fix)** `searchStores()` had `firstSetStoreButton.waitFor({ timeout: 15_000 })`. Firefox/WebKit store search API responses took >15s. Fix: increased to 30s.\n62: \n63: ---\n64: \n65: ## Wait Strategy Inventory\n66: \n67: | Flow | Strategy |\n68: |---|---|\n69: | Newsletter section appears | `scrollTo(document.body.scrollHeight)` × 2, retry loop (15×1s), `scrollIntoViewIfNeeded`, final `waitFor(45s)` |\n70: | Newsletter button | `click({ force: true })` to bypass overlay |\n71: | Login form | `BasePage.navigate()` + `networkidle(20s)` + `body.click({force})` + `waitFor(45s)` |\n72: | Store selector opens | `scrollIntoViewIfNeeded` + 2.5s wait + try/catch 5s → fallback 15s |\n73: | Store search results | `waitFor({ timeout: 30_000 })` on first Set Store button |\n74: \n75: ---\n76: \n77: ## Open Questions\n78: \n79: | # | Question | Impact |\n80: |---|---|---|"}}
